714464f.title: Manhattan: 75th Street (West) - Amsterdam Avenue
714464f.text:
West 75th Street, west from but not including Amsterdam Ave. Intersection
shown in the foreground is Broadway.
July 27, 1936.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.

715953f-a.title: Manhattan: Amsterdam Avenue - 75th Street (West)
715953f-a.text:
Amsterdam .ve., east side, north from and including West 75th., to,
but not including West 76th Streets. Also shown is West 75th Street, north
side, east from Amsterdam, to, but not including Columbus Aves. Proninent
building shown at the N.E. corner, is No. 161 West 75th Street.
About 1928.
Khickerbocker Photo Service.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
